						 <p>These are just some suggestions with word choice, im not saying you have to or should use this advice, they're just suggestions.</p> <blockquote> <p>The anomalous effect triggers</p> </blockquote> <p>instead of triggers, use activates</p> <blockquote> <p>raw meat and a human being,</p> </blockquote> <p>Organic material, usually animal tissue and a human subject</p> <p>Anesthetic gas making the prime subject unconscious for a period of around 14-16 hours</p> 
